The Jeevas were an English rock band. Its members were Crispian Mills (vocals, guitar), Andy Nixon (drums), and Dan McKinna (bass).

Mills was previously the vocalist of Kula Shaker. Nixon and McKinna are previous members of the band, Straw. Mills rejoined Kula Shaker in late 2005, and The Jeevas disbanded.

Nixon and McKinna have formed a new group called The Magic Bullet Band. They toured in support of the Kula Shaker reunion tour in early 2006, but have yet to release any recorded material.
